

    #   Typically the configuration is divided into multiple layers #20
    
    #   An Example
        
        Presentation Layer          beans-web.xml       ConfigurationForWeb class 
        Business/Service Layer      beans-service.xml   CofigurationForService
        Data Access Layer           beans-dao.xml       CofigurationForDao
        Container Specific Layer    beans-config.xml    ConfigurationForConfig
        Security Layer              beans-security.xml  ConfigurationForSecurity